'''''Fiela's Child''''' ni ikinamico yo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika y'Epfo]] yanditswe na Dalene Matthee kandi yasohotse mu 1985<ref>Fiela's Child Study Guide | GradeSaver <nowiki>https://www.gradesaver.com</nowiki> › fielas-child</ref>. Igitabo cyanditswe mbere muri [[Ikinyafurikansi|Afrikaans]] ku izina rya '''''Fiela se Kind''''', nyuma kiza guhindurwa mu [[Icyongereza|Cyongereza]], [[Igifaransa]], [[Ikidage]], [[Icyesipanyole|Icyesipanyoli]], igitaliyani, Igiheburayo, Isilande na Sinhalese, n'ibindi<ref name=":0">Fiela's Child - Dubray Books <nowiki>https://www.dubraybooks.ie</nowiki> › fielas-child_9780582287...</ref><ref name=":0" />.

== Insanganyamatsiko ==
Matthee akemura ibibazo by’ibidukikije, insanganyamatsiko zishingiye ku ivanguramoko no kuvangura amoko. blue-buck burenze guhigwa kandi inzovu ziricwa<ref>Fiela's Child (Forest, book 2) by Dalene Matthee - Fantastic ... <nowiki>https://www.fantasticfiction.com</nowiki> › Dalene Matthee</ref> . Umubano hagati y'abazungu nabandi birabura uragoye<ref>Fiela's Child by Matthee, Dalene - Penguin Random House ... <nowiki>https://www.penguinrandomhouse.co.za</nowiki> › fielas-child</ref>. Nubwo ibi mbere ya Apartheid mugihe tekiniki habaye uburinganire imbere y amategeko, gahunda y'amategeko yabogamye kandi ishyigikira abazungu. Inganda zo mu nyanja zibabajwe no kwinjiza amato akoreshwa na parike<ref>'Fiela's Child': Tallinn Review - Screen Daily <nowiki>https://www.screendaily.com</nowiki> › reviews › 5144975.article</ref>.

== Ibice byo kugarukira ==
Mu gitabo cyanditswe na Dalene Matthee icyerekezo cyo kugarukira, aho umuntu abasha guhitamo uwo ari we n'icyo agomba kuba afite, uruhare runini. Mu gitabo<ref>Fiela's Child (Fiela se Kind) Summary and Study Guide <nowiki>https://www.supersummary.com</nowiki> › fielas-child › summary</ref>, Benjamini ari mu ntera ntarengwa kandi ntazi umwirondoro we. Na none, igenamiterere risobanurwa ko riri murwego ntarengwa bityo bibera kumpande zombi z'umusozi <ref>Fiela's Child - Paper Plus <nowiki>https://www.paperplus.co.nz</nowiki> › non-fiction › fielas-child</ref> .

== Filime ==
Igitabo cyakozwe muri firime mu 1988 gikinwamo Shaleen Surtie-Richards nka Fiela. <ref>[https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0144200/maindetails Fiela se Kind (1988)]</ref> Filime muri 2019 yakinnye na Zenobia Kloppers nka Fiela.
